<p class="ko" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">출처: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D., &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. 테라(Terra)/UST 디페깅 타임라인은 Chainalysis, Richmond Fed Economic Brief(2022), 온체인 공개 데이터를 참고해 필자가 정리. 2020년 3월 12일 비트코인 가격 및 청산 규모는 비트멕스(BitMEX) 공개 데이터 기준.</p>
<p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D., &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. The Terra/UST depegging timeline was compiled by the author from Chainalysis, the Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022), and public on-chain data. Bitcoin's March 12, 2020 price action and liquidation figures are based on publicly reported BitMEX data.</p>
<p class="ja" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">出典: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190。Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107。Giné, X., Karlan, D., &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235。テラ(Terra)/USTのデペッグのタイムラインは、Chainalysis、Richmond Fed Economic Brief(2022年)、オンチェーン公開データを基に筆者が整理。2020年3月12日のビットコイン価格および清算規模はビットメックス(BitMEX)の公開データに基づく。</p>
<p class="es" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fuentes: Rottenstreich, Y. y Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D., y Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. La cronología del depeg de Terra/UST fue compilada por el autor a partir de Chainalysis, el Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) y datos públicos on-chain. Los datos de precio y liquidaciones de bitcoin del 12 de marzo de 2020 se basan en datos públicos de BitMEX.</p>
<p class="de" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Quellen: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. Die Terra/UST-Depegging-Zeitlinie wurde vom Autor anhand von Chainalysis, dem Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) und öffentlichen On-Chain-Daten zusammengestellt. Bitcoins Kursverlauf und Liquidationszahlen vom 12. März 2020 basieren auf öffentlich zugänglichen BitMEX-Daten.</p>
<p class="fr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources : Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), « Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk », Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), « Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law », Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), « Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation », American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. La chronologie du décrochage Terra/UST a été compilée par l'auteur à partir de Chainalysis, du Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) et de données on-chain publiques. Les données de prix et de liquidations du bitcoin du 12 mars 2020 reposent sur des données BitMEX publiques.</p>
<p class="pt" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fontes: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. A linha do tempo do desatrelamento Terra/UST foi compilada pelo autor a partir da Chainalysis, do Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) e de dados on-chain públicos. Os dados de preço e liquidação do bitcoin de 12 de março de 2020 se baseiam em dados públicos da BitMEX.</p>
<p class="tr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Kaynaklar: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. Terra/UST sabitlik kaybı zaman çizelgesi yazar tarafından Chainalysis, Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) ve kamuya açık on-chain verilerden derlenmiştir. 12 Mart 2020 bitcoin fiyat hareketi ve tasfiye rakamları kamuya açık BitMEX verilerine dayanmaktadır.</p>
<p class="vi" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Nguồn: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D., &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. Dòng thời gian mất chốt Terra/UST do tác giả tổng hợp từ Chainalysis, Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) và dữ liệu on-chain công khai. Dữ liệu giá bitcoin và quy mô thanh lý ngày 12/3/2020 dựa trên dữ liệu công khai của BitMEX.</p>
<p class="id" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sumber: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D., &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. Garis waktu depeg Terra/UST disusun penulis dari Chainalysis, Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022), dan data on-chain publik. Data harga bitcoin dan skala likuidasi 12 Maret 2020 berdasarkan data publik BitMEX.</p>
<p class="pl" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Źródła: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. Oś czasu odpięcia Terra/UST została zestawiona przez autora na podstawie Chainalysis, Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) oraz publicznych danych on-chain. Dane o cenie bitcoina i skali likwidacji z 12 marca 2020 roku opierają się na publicznie dostępnych danych BitMEX.</p>
<p class="it" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fonti: Rottenstreich, Y. &amp; Hsee, C.K. (2001), "Money, Kisses, and Electric Shocks: On the Affective Psychology of Risk," Psychological Science, 12(3), 185-190. Sunstein, C.R. (2002), "Probability Neglect: Emotions, Worst Cases, and Law," Yale Law Journal, 112(1), 61-107. Giné, X., Karlan, D. &amp; Zinman, J. (2010), "Put Your Money Where Your Butt Is: A Commitment Contract for Smoking Cessation," American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 2(4), 213-235. La cronologia del de-peg Terra/UST è stata compilata dall'autore a partire da Chainalysis, dal Richmond Fed Economic Brief (2022) e da dati on-chain pubblici. I dati sul prezzo del bitcoin e sull'entità delle liquidazioni del 12 marzo 2020 si basano su dati pubblici di BitMEX.</p>
